Package: allocator
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative Investment Analytics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alejandro Sotolongo
Maintainer: Alejandro Sotolongo <asotolongo@diversifiedtrust.com>
Description: Allocator is a collection of functions for asset allocators to 
    analyze investment returns and holdings. The functions are designed for 
    workflows that include downloading and reading in data, performance
    analytics, portfolio construction, and risk weight analysis.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: xts, lubridate, timeDate, bizdays, R6, PerformanceAnalytics, ggplot2
